data.description: Welcome Home! Centrally located in Rocky Ford is this well maintained 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home with original hardwood floors throughout. The large basement with wet bar can be your canvas for creating a space for what will meet your wants and needs. Spend your time outside on the back deck easily accessible from the back of the home providing plenty of entertaining space. Take advantage of the new solar system that produces enough electricity to sustain the home and no longer worry about your monthly electric bill. The NEW roof has a transferrable warranty and other recent upgrades include a new A/C unit, electrical wiring in the basement, plumbing work, and fresh exterior paint. The ring doorbell and security system will stay with the home. This house has passed an FHA appraisal and is currently listed below the APPRAISED VALUE.
